PLAIN-ENGLISH SUMMARY
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

You can install this kit, modify it, and use it for your own personal use
or your own business operations. You can read every file, fork it for
your own purposes, and share what you learn from using it.

You can't repackage this kit and sell it as a product, host it as a
service for others to use, or distribute a competing kit derived from
this one. Those rights are reserved.

