═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

1. PERMITTED USE

   You may install, modify, and use the Partner AI Kit (and any
   derivative work based on it) for any of the following:

   a) Your own personal use.
   b) Your own organization's internal operations, including
      commercial operations of your own business.
   c) Educational, research, and learning purposes.
   d) Sharing your install experience publicly (blog posts, social
      media, video walkthroughs) provided you credit the source per
      Section 3.

2. RESTRICTED USE

   Without prior written permission from the copyright holder, you may NOT:

   a) Sell, sublicense, or otherwise distribute the Partner AI Kit
      (or any derivative work) as a standalone product or kit.
   b) Provide the Partner AI Kit (or any derivative work) as a hosted
      service, SaaS offering, or managed agent product to third
      parties.
   c) Use the "Partner AI Kit" name, branding, or trade dress in any
      product or service you distribute.
   d) Distribute a competing product or kit that is substantially
      derived from this work.

   For clarity: a Training Club, freelancer, agency, or other business
   using the Partner AI Kit internally — even as part of a commercial
   operation — is permitted under Section 1(b). The restrictions apply
   only to redistribution, resale, hosting-for-others, and competing
   distribution.

3. ATTRIBUTION

